==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tiglic
<hw>Tig"lic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Of,
pertaining to, or designating, an acid, <chform>C4H7CO2H</chform>
(called also <xex>methyl crotonic acid</xex>), homologous with crotonic
acid, and obtained from croton oil (from <spn>Croton Tiglium</spn>) as a
white crystalline substance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tigress</ent>⟦br⟧
